Frequently Asked Questions

1. CAN YOU SHIP TO COUNTRIES OUTSIDE OF INDIA THROUGH A FREIGHT FORWARDING ADDRESS?

At this time, we are only able to ship to addresses within INDIA, and we cannot accept freight forwarding addresses.

2. WHAT CURRENCY ARE ITEMS DISPLAYED IN?

All items on the StyleCabbie website are displayed in INDIAN currency only.

3. CAN I USE MY STYLE CABBIE GIFT CARD TOWARD MY ONLINE ORDER?

You may redeem StyleCabbies eGift cards at StyleCabbies online store.

4. DOES MY STYLECABBIEs GIFT CARD AND PROMOTIONAL GIFT CARD EXPIRE?

Purchased StyleCabbie eGift cards do not expire. Promotional cards issued by StyleCabbie often have expiration dates. Please check the terms and conditions of the specific promotion.

5. HOW CAN I CHECK THE BALANCE OF MY STYLECABBIE eGIFT CARD OR PROMOTIONAL GIFT CARD?

To check your balance, please click on this link

6. HOW DO I PURCHASE AN ITEM I SAW ON YOUR SITE, WHICH IS NOT AVAILABLE FOR SALE ONLINE?

You may contact us at Customer Care and an associate will be pleased to assist you with your inquiry.

7. WHEN I ADD AN ITEM TO MY SHOPPING CART, IS THE ITEM RESERVED FOR ME UNTIL I DECIDE TO PLACE MY ORDER?

Items added to your shopping cart are not reserved until you place your order. To avoid being disappointed, we encourage you to place your order once you are certain of your intent to purchase it. Please note fulfillment of items within your order is not guaranteed until you receive a shipping confirmation email.

8. CAN I MODIFY MY ONLINE ORDER?

We begin to process orders immediately, so we may be unable to make any changes. For further assistance, please contact Customer Care.

9. WILL ALL ITEMS IN MY ORDER ARRIVE IN THE SAME SHIPMENT?

Orders placed on StyleCabbie.com may ship from our distribution centre. You may receive your items in multiple shipments. You will not be charged multiple shipping fees, if shipping fees are applicable to your one order.

10. CAN I RETURN MY STYLECABBIE.COM PICK UP ORDER AFTER PICK UP?

Please read our Return Policy. Your order number and pick up confirmation will be required to process the return.

11. HOW DO I PLACE MY ORDER?

Once you have decided on the specific product that youd like to purchase from us, please select the Size that you wish to buy.
TIP: Use the size chart on every product page placed below to the size to choose the right size.

Select Add to Bag to add the product to your cart. If there are other products that youd like to buy from us, continue shopping.
TIP: Click Qty if you want to buy multiple products of the same type.

Select Place Order to buy the product. Submit your shipping address, select a mode of payment, and confirm your order by making the payment.
TIP: Pay online to get a 10% StyleCabbie Coupon . Shop for more than Rs.1000 to get free shipping.

Cashback on prepaid orders will get credited to your next purchase once the order gets shipped.

12. MY ORDER IS NOT YET PACKED/SHIPPED?

Since our website is not a marketplace and all the products we sell are manufactured by us. We conduct quality checks before we send out a product to you so you get the best with every order you place. So, it may take anywhere between 4 to 5 working days before the shipment goes out from our warehouse. If this is not the case then please share your query in detail along with the order id number. Our Customer Care executive will work on your query. We will get back to you in the next 24 hours.

13. HOW DO I KNOW IF MY ORDER WAS SUCCESSFULLY PLACED?

Once your order is placed, you can find details of your order:
The order confirmation page
E-mail confirmation sent to your registered E-mail id.
The order confirmation page you will be directed to after placing your order Email confirmation sent to your registered e-mail id.
SMS confirmation sent to your registered mobile number.
We will send you another confirmation once we ship your order.

14. What are the charges that will apply on my order?

We ensure there are no hidden charges in our entire checkout process
Free shipping on all prepaid orders
COD charges of 25 per product if you choose cash-on-delivery as your mode of payment.
The price of the products you see are inclusive of taxes.

15. WHY CANT I SEE THE CASH-ON-DELIVERY (COD) OPTION?

In a few pincodes, we are unable to provide the cash-on-delivery payment option currently. You may however, use for any other mode of payment such as Debit Card, Credit Card, or using an Online Wallet.
You may have defaulted in receiving your items and/or making any payments when the carrier person came to deliver your order package at your destination.

16. I AM UNABLE TO ADD PRODUCTS TO MY CART?

Contact our customer service at Customer Care, executive and we will resolve this. Well get back to you within 24 hours:

17. MY ORDER STATUS IS SHOWING ORDER SHIPPED BUT NOT YET DELIVERED?

We apologise for the inconvenience. Please share your query in detail along with the order id number, our Customer Care executive will work on your query . We will get back to you in the next 24 hours.

18. I HAVE NOT RECEIVED AN ORDER CONFIRMATION EMAIL OR NOTIFICATIONS?

Please check your order has been placed on the My Orders page
Dont worry, you will receive a confirmation e-mail and SMS soon within 12 hours.
Please check your spam folder as well.
After 12 hours, please contact the Customer Care executive and we will help in looking into the issue.

19. HOW DO I WANT TO CHANGE MY DELIVERY ADDRESS OR PHONE NUMBERS?

If your order has been shipped we will not be able to make any changes in the delivery address. We can inform our courier partner to send the shipment back to us by contacting us at Customer Care executive. Please share the order id number and let us know the next course of action. Will try our best to help you out. Thank You.

20. THE ORDER I HAVE RECEIVED IS NOT WHAT I EXPECTED. WHAT SHOULD I DO?
Were extremely sorry for the inconvenience caused. Please reach out to us below with the following info:

21. I WASNT AVAILABLE AT THE TIME OF THE DELIVERY, BUT I WANT MY ORDER. WHAT SHOULD I DO?

Contact our Customer Care executive, to resolve this. Well get back to you within 24 hours.

22. I TRIED TO MAKE A TRANSACTION,BUT IT FAILED. WHAT DO I DO?

If the amount has been deducted from your bank or card, don’t worry; it will be refunded to the same account within 7-10 business days.

Meanwhile, please wait a while and try again, preferably using a different payment method.
These are the payment methods we accept:

Debit Card
Credit Card
Net banking
Leading e-wallets
For any further inquiries, please feel free to contact our Customer Care executive. Well get back to you within 24 hours.

23. MY TRANSACTION FAILED BUT AN AMOUNT WAS DEDUCTED FROM MY SC WALLET. WHAT DO I DO?

If your wallet amount has been deducted the same will be credited back in your SC wallet within a couple of hours

24. WHEN WILL I RECEIVE CASHBACK OF MY ORDER?

Prepaid order cashback will get credited to your SC wallet once the order gets shipped
Also for products that are already discounted, loyalty amount will not be applicable to the design of the day and factory outlet products.

25. I HAVE LOYALTY MONEY IN MY SC WALLET. CAN I TRANSFER IT TO MY BANK ACCOUNT?

No. The Loyalty Money is associated with your StyleCabbie account only, and cannot be en-cashed or transferred to other accounts.

26. CAN I PAY USING AN INTERNATIONAL CARD?

We currently do not accept payment via international cards.

27.I HAVE SELF-SHIPPED. HOW DO I GET THE REFUND?

If you have self-shipped the product already, please email us the screenshot of the courier receipt along with the order id number.

Our Customer Care executive will work on your query. We will get back to you in the next 24 hours.

28. WILL STYLECABBIE.COM EMPLOYEE ASK FOR MY CONFIDENTIAL INFORMATION?

Stylecabbie.com employees will never ask for your credentials like StyleCabbie password, OTP, Credit/Debit card expiry and CVV or any other confidential information except for your name, address, e-mail id and mobile number.

29. IM HAVING A TECHNICAL ISSUE WITH YOUR WEBSITE. CAN YOU HELP ME RESOLVE THIS?

The StyleCabbie website has been tested to work on multiple devices and browsers. However, you may find that switching to a different browser, deleting cookies and/or cache may resolve the technical issue you are experiencing.
If you still continue to experience the error, please contact the Customer Care executive. You may need to provide information about your device and browser for our team to troubleshoot, so please ensure this information is available.

30. DOES STYLECABBIE OFFER PRICE ADJUSTMENTS ON PREVIOUSLY-PURCHASED MERCHANDISE OR PRICE MATCHING?

StyleCabbie does not offer price adjustments on previously purchased merchandise or price matching with other retailers.
